  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BigFraction
    An immutable representation of a rational number as a fraction with BigInteger-valued numerator and denominator, in reduced normal form.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidFractionException
    An exception indicating an invalid BigFraction.
    InvalidProbabilityException
    An exception indicating that a value is not a probability.
